RegionSphere           package:NeuroImage           R Documentation

_c_r_e_a_t_i_o_n _f_u_n_c_t_i_o_n _f_o_r _S_p_h_e_r_i_c _B_r_a_i_n_R_e_g_i_o_n_3_D

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     creates a new BrainRegion3D instance with a spheric geometry.

_U_s_a_g_e:

             RegionSphere(bvol, centroid, radius)    

_A_r_g_u_m_e_n_t_s:

    bvol: the 'BrainVolume' that on which the geometry of the region is
          based 

centroid: the center coordinates (in grid space) of the region 

  radius: the radius of the sphere of the constructed region 

